HEADWORD: Termes
<hw>Ter"mes</hw> <pr>(t⟦etil⟧r"m⟦emac⟧z)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>;
<plu><it>pl.</it> <plw>Termites</plw> <pr>(-m⟦icr⟧*t⟦emac⟧z)</pr>.</plu>
